SOURCES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LINDA BURUM 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 After visiting several markets reputed to carry Malay products, I found Shun 
Fat in Monterey Park had the best selection.It carries various brands of 
Malaysian-style curry powder, the fermented shrimp preparations belacan and 
petis udang , and spicy sambals , as well as the necessary dry spices for curry 
and the rice noodle soup, laksa . Most items are in the Indonesian section, but 
some are found in a separate curry section along with the general seasonings. 
</P>
<P>
 In the "wet" department you'll find lengkuas , (the ginger-like rhizome known 
as galangal in English), lemon grass and Asian basil. 
</P>
<P>
 Shun Fat Supermarket, 421 N. Atlantic Blvd., Monterey Park. (818) 308-9880.  
</P>
<P>
 LINDA BURUM 
</P>
