</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 25, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 5; Column 1; Op-Ed Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
