<P>
 The Rams updated the injury status of cornerback Darryl Henley Thursday, 
listing him as questionable rather than out of Sunday's game with the Chargers 
in San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
 Henley, who injured a hip flexor, ran at practice, but did not participate. 
</P>
