 Wide receiver Flipper Anderson, who is listed as probable because of a thigh 
injury, also did not practice. 
</P>
<P>
 The Chargers added defensive tackle Shawn Lee to their injury report with a 
calf injury. Quarterback Stan Humphries, who is listed as questionable because 
of an elbow injury, practiced for the second day in a row, but reported more 
soreness. T.J. SIMERS 
