boards. Inoue returns to direct the offense, which lacks scoring punch, 
especially from the outside. Taylor is hoping Inoue and Haneef will pick up the 
offensive load with McBride adding some perimeter scoring ability. Taylor is 
optimistic the Hawks will improve over last season. It figures to take a leap 
