<TEXT>
<P>
 Help for Entrepreneurs: If you're an entrepreneur in Orange County looking for 
ideas to help expand your business, now is the time to give Cal State 
Fullerton's Small Business Institute a call.The institute is looking to sign up 
small businesses for its free counseling program. The program matches an 
entrepreneur with three to six graduate business students, who with the help of 
a Cal State faculty member provide ideas, data and other resources to help 
businesses grow. The program runs for 12 weeks, and the next session begins in 
the spring. To be considered, call (714) 773-2251 by Jan. 20. 
