<DOCNO> LA112594-0168 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 102053 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 25, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
